==English==

===Pronunciation===
* {{SAMPA|/baImIlEni@l/}}

===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[bimillennialis]]'' from ''[[bi]]'' "two" ''mill-'' "thousand" + ''[[ennius|enni(us)]]'' "yearly".

===Noun===
'''bimillennial'''
# The 2,000th [[anniversary]] of an event or happening.

===Adjective===
'''bimillennial'''
# Occuring every thousand (2,000) [[year]]s and 2 [[millennium|millennia]].

